  "title": "Field screening of chickpea genotypes for resistance to the root-knot disease caused by Meloidogyne spp in Nepal",
  "abstract": "During 1987-88, 267 chickpea genotypes were screened for resistance to M. javanica and M. incognita race 2. T11-1 and NEC321 were considered the least susceptible, with fewer than 50 galls/root.",
